room_title: Escape room "Diamond Heist" by Hawaii Escape Challenge in Honolulu
room_description: An international master thief has stolen a rare and priceless diamond. Your group has been hired by a high profile client to recover it. After months of tracking the thief, you have discovered he keeps it somewhere in his hillside mansion. The thief has left for exactly 60 minutes. Get in the thief's residence, locate the diamond and get out without being noticed!
